{"tid":2378224,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE MOMO尺度大開 只穿內衣解放傲人上圍馬甲線","createTime":"2021-01-24T09:43:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T11:05:22.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":78,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"0ee2f5a5154990a80e0036056bbd715f84ae3320","tid":2378224,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T09:43:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2021-01-24/1024/20210124002649.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2021-01-24%2F1024%2F20210124002649.jpg&h=ffb4bf20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTWICE MOMO近日在IG上曬出辣照，引網友暴動。（圖／IG@twicetagram）<br />\n<br />\n南韓女子天團TWICE，繼去年底發行韓文數位單曲《CRY FOR ME》後人氣再度飆升。行程滿檔的她們，日前宣布即將在3月舉行日本線上演唱會並在網路上曬出「9人合體」的宣傳照，令粉絲們開心不已。另外，日籍成員MOMO近日也在官方IG上曬出性感辣照，同樣引爆話題。<br />\n<br />\nTWICE出道5年，憑著甜美清純的形象在歌壇中快速竄紅，近期一連在「首爾歌謠大賞」、「2020 MAMA」、「金唱片獎」等頒獎典禮上獲得音樂大獎，成績獲得肯定。但自從Mina及定延陸續傳出健康問題停工，加上Sana一度因疫情遭到隔離後，TWICE便一直呈現9缺1甚至缺2的情況，直到日前透過經紀公司公開她們將於今年3月舉行的日本線上演唱會「TWICE in Wonderland」宣傳照，才再次看到9人合體。<br />\n<br />\n另外，一直都以超群舞技著稱的日籍成員MOMO，近日在官方IG公開的ㄧ組辣照也同樣吸睛。照片中，MOMO先是PO出一套「中空裝」造型，以平口針織背心搭配蘇格蘭百褶短裙及鹅黃色的小外套，看起來俏皮又不失性感；隨後，MOMO換上一件黑色運動內衣搭配同色系三角短褲，並以外套綁在腰間勾勒腰線，大方秀出傲人的上圍曲線及超狂腹肌，令粉絲們大噴鼻血。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/twicetagram/?utm_source=ig_embed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftwicetagram%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCP8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=7a9759f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/twicetagram/?utm_source=ig_embed</a><br />\n<br />\n原來MOMO近日受到邀請，為日本實力派新人歌手yukaDD擔任新歌《Superhero》的MV女主角，並在其中一連換上4套造型，甜美又性感的風格MOMO皆成功駕馭，曼妙的身形也讓網友們直呼「MOMO的身材太好了」、「愛死她了，又甜又性感」。"},{"pid":"eaded4f837f0dec0076aee74f8e340cf028a1fb3","tid":2378224,"uid":16659,"like":11,"dislike":58,"score":-47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T09:43:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EsU4RnlXEAE_ZiZ?format=jpg&amp;name=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEsU4RnlXEAE_ZiZ%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dmedium&h=01517475&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EsU4RnmW8AAHQU-?format=jpg&amp;name=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEsU4RnmW8AAHQU-%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dmedium&h=6eeaefc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EsU4RnoW4AAm1xM?format=jpg&amp;name=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEsU4RnoW4AAm1xM%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dmedium&h=33da8e2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EsU4RnnXUAA9duz?format=jpg&amp;name=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEsU4RnnXUAA9duz%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dmedium&h=144826bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7b56339622ee7a4c6c29499d57b5cc4748e6d3a","tid":2378224,"uid":339805,"like":90,"dislike":3,"score":87,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T09:44:37.000Z","msg":"希澈老師：我咩都睇過晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f3fb06ed6a64d8bf65cc07a2f79c96e01699610","tid":2378224,"uid":320204,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c7b56339622ee7a4c6c29499d57b5cc4748e6d3a","tid":2378224,"uid":339805,"like":90,"dislike":3,"score":87,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T09:44:37.000Z","msg":"希澈老師：我咩都睇過晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T09:45:03.000Z","msg":"你收聲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2111ca670faaeb0633440a41db1f92da05336770","tid":2378224,"uid":261849,"like":4,"dislike":14,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T09:45:15.000Z","msg":"佢真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日本妹無得頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f108